《'''One Spring Day'''》是韓國男子偶像團體[[2AM|2AM]]第二張韓語專輯<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.allkpop.com/2013/02/2am-releases-details-and-tracklist-for-anticipated-return-with-one-spring-day | title = 2AM releases details and tracklist for anticipated return with ‘One Spring Day’ | publisher = allkpop | date = 2013-02-21 | accessdate = 2014-03-21 | archive-date = 2013-02-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130224063513/http://www.allkpop.com/2013/02/2am-releases-details-and-tracklist-for-anticipated-return-with-one-spring-day | dead-url = no }}</ref>，在2013年3月5日推出。在這專輯中，2AM計劃為其音樂轉型，歌曲預告介紹中[[任瑟雍|任瑟雍]]的聲音變得突出和不同<ref>{{cite web | url = http://enewsworld.mnet.com/enews/contents.asp?idx=28619 | title = http://enewsworld.mnet.com/enews/contents.asp?idx=28619 | publisher = enewsworld | date = 2013-02-11 | accessdate = 2014-03-21 | archive-date = 2013-04-11 | archive-url = https://archive.today/20130411091318/http://enewsworld.mnet.com/enews/contents.asp?idx=28619 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。使用緩慢的鋼琴旋律的主打歌《某個春日》（{{lang-ko|어느 봄날}}） 隨著首支預告片在2013年1月27日發布<ref>{{cite news|last=Lee|first=Gyeong-Ho|title=2AM release the new song “One Spring Day"|url=http://star.mt.co.kr/stviewEng.php?type=3&no=2013022709065497446|accessdate=13 May 2013|newspaper=Star News|date=27 February 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140321043126/http://star.mt.co.kr/stviewEng.php?type=3&no=2013022709065497446|archivedate=2014年3月21日}}</ref>。

